30:46.950 --> 30:48.380
thank you.

30:48.420 --> 30:49.580
jim francis?

30:49.620 --> 30:50.520
yeah.

30:50.550 --> 30:51.620
hi. i'm brenda.

30:51.650 --> 30:52.550
okay.

