30:54.980 --> 30:56.180
okay.

30:56.220 --> 30:58.420
now, how long ago were you released from prison?

30:58.450 --> 31:01.050
uh...about eight months ago.

31:01.080 --> 31:04.080
and how long have you been in a.a.?

31:04.120 --> 31:07.420
about eight months...off and on.

31:07.450 --> 31:09.050
are you drunk right now?

31:10.380 --> 31:12.820
um, define "drunk."

31:14.750 --> 31:16.680
