i just told commander taylor to arrange a press conferrence

39:41.640 --> 39:43.570
for the first thing in the morning

39:43.870 --> 39:45.800
let the world to know the meihans has nothing to do with this

39:46.330 --> 39:47.650
if you don't mind i think richard will

39:47.780 --> 39:49.230
handle this one

